+ *
+ * Deletes the structure *@structure.  At the end, *@structure is set
+ * to NULL.
+ *
+ * Returns: %ASN1_SUCCESS if successful, %ASN1_ELEMENT_NOT_FOUND if
+ *   *@structure was NULL.
