+/* Description: change the field TYPE of an NODE_ASN element.     */
+/*              The new value is the old one | (bitwise or) the   */
+/*              paramener VALUE.                                  */
+/* Parameters:                                                    */
+/*   node: NODE_ASN element pointer.                              */
+/*   value: the integer value that must be or-ed with the current */
+/*          value of field TYPE.                                  */
+/* Return: NODE pointer.                                          */
